Its elegant curves and detailed band are reminiscent of the intricate designs of the early 20th century, making it an ideal choice for those who are drawn to romance and nostalgia.

column1: The Luna Set With A 1 Carat Emerald Lab Diamond
column3: The Luna is a stunning solitaire with petal prongs that delicately embrace the center stone, giving it a touch of nature-inspired charm. The graceful lines and subtle curves allow the diamond to shine with an unparalleled luminosity, reflecting both the light and the depth of your commitment. Whether you choose a classic round cut or a more contemporary shape for your stone, The Luna always catches the eye and showcases the beauty of your love.

column1: The Amber Set With A 1 Carat Elongated Cushion Lab Diamond
column3: The Amber is a gorgeous engagement ring in an ornate-style setting, decorated with romantic milgrain detailing and additional engraving on the ring's head. An esthetic choice that combines the fine details of a vintage ring with the comfort of a smooth-polish solitaire band.

column1: The Pave Charlotte Set With A 1 Carat Elongated Cushion Lab Diamond
column3: With stunning shine and a smooth modern silhouette, The pave Charlotte brings the sleekness of the classic bevel to new heights. A gorgeous pave band makes way for a spectacular hidden halo. Just below, a diamond bridge lays under a unique peekaboo window highlighting the underside of your stone to let in light while surrounding it with sparkle from every angle. Striking on its own, the high setting is also ideal for future stacking or nesting closely with the perfect wedding band.
